ActTransportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of J. RICHARD W. HALL of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a full-time member of the Transportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; and designation of J.
